			quoteText="We provide superannuation administration services to superannuation trustees and administrators and also takes care of administrative tasks for advisors through experience and technical innovation. we deliver these services at lower cost to you so you can focus on other important stuff."
			customerName="Liberty Superannuation"
		/>
		<TextAndImageHero reversed>
			<div slot="text-container">
				<h1>Who we are</h1>
				<h3>Trusted advisor</h3>
				<p>Liberty super is your trusted advisor when it comes
					to self managed superannuation matters including
					tax compliance, admin, and investment strategy.</p>
				<h3>Technological partner</h3>
				<p>Liberty super provides strong technological
					development skillsets to help you build up your own
					capabilities to add value to your current client base
					via efficient and optimum solutions, without adding
					to your operating cost.</p>
			</div>
